# ShivOS Technology Decision

| Component | Selected Technology | Source |
|------------|---------------------|--------|
| Android Base | AOSP | Google |
| Raspberry Pi Support | KonstaKANG Concepts | Community |
| Architecture | GloDroid Philosophy | GloDroid |
| Kernel | Linux Mainline (when practical) | Linux |
| Graphics | Mesa 3D | Mesa |
| Hardware Composer | drm_hwcomposer | Android-x86 |
| Buffer Manager | minigbm | GloDroid |
| Bootloader | U-Boot | Standard |
| OTA | A/B Updates | Android |
| Security | SELinux | Android |
| Encryption | FBE | Android |
| Desktop UI | Custom ShivOS Desktop | ShivOS |
| Launcher | Launcher3 Modified | Android |
| AI Framework | NNAPI + Future Local AI | ShivOS |

## Engineering Principles

- Keep framework clean.
- Avoid unnecessary hacks.
- Prefer open-source technologies.
- Build for portability.
- Optimize for Raspberry Pi first.
- Future support for ARM devices.